high_descs: Turn left and veer left to the sink.
Pick up the ladle to the right of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the counter in front of you.
Place the ladle in the bowl on the left.
Pick up the bowl.
Turn right and veer right to the microwave.
Place the bowl in the right top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a ladle in it in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and move to the right of the sink
Grab the spoon that is on the counter
Turn around and go straight to the counter
Place the spoon inside the bowl on the counter
Pick up the bowl with the spoon inside it
Turn to the right and get to the microwave
Place the bowl inside the second cabinet above the microwave
anns.task_desc: Putting a bowl inside a cabinet

high_descs: Turn left and begin towards the kitchen counter, then hang a left and walk over to the counter area to the right of the kitchen sink.
Pick up the large metal spoon that is on the counter to the right of the kitchen sink.
Turn around and walk ahead to the kitchen counter with a glass bowl sitting there.
Place the large metal spoon handle up into the glass bowl.
Pick up the glass bowl with the metal spoon in it.
Turn around and walk back towards the sink, then hang a left and walk over to the microwave.
Place the glass bowl with the metal spoon in it into the upper cabinet that is the second cabinet from the left.
anns.task_desc: Place a glass bowl with a spoon in it into an upper kitchen cabinet.
